Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 流星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 又看到流星了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 下次许个愿望看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的流星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是神在打开天空的盖子时漏出来的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那时许愿的话 神就会听到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.65,0:00:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多愿望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成为护士 也想去宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.82,0:00:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟哥哥说也没用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要向星星大人请求才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 星星大人 星星大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:00:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.93,0:01:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 快关掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰到各位了 请多包涵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也给我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里稍候再打扫 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.02,0:01:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据这影像中的情报整理显示
